    narr:generatedFrom "3f1c9f1c2f23299d1e0f789786004ffd72085b32" ;
    narr:narration """This hub documents a consistent rhetorical register centered on the direct, first-person founder voice, primarily Scarlet's, which functions as the system's primary evidentiary layer. The mainline is unhedged and declarative, utilizing [direct correction](narr:Style_DirectCorrection) to replace faulty claims and [imperative rules](narr:StyleObs_DirectImperative) to define policy. Authenticity is signaled through [Markdown blockquotes](narr:StyleObs_BlockquoteVoice) that isolate founder speech from analytical prose, treating these transcripts as [primary data](narr:StyleObs_DirectQuoteEvidence) rather than anecdote. The tone frequently incorporates [profanity as a decisiveness marker](narr:StyleObs_ProfanityDecisiveness) and employs [em-dash pivots](narr:StyleObs_EmDashRhetoric) to deliver punchy, staccato verdicts. A parallel [second-person mode](narr:StyleObs_SecondPerson) maintains a constant focus on the prospect or AI coworker, while [metaphorical frameworks](narr:StyleObs_5)—notably the optometrist model of iterative convergence—structure the technical and strategic discourse. Recent entries have expanded this register to include [vulnerable personal narrative](narr:StyleObs_VulnerableRegister) and [identity-grounded positioning](narr:StyleObs_QueerFirstPersonVoice), marking a shift from purely strategic communication toward a more intimate, founder-led brand idiolect.""" ;
